description: The report, commissioned by Scouting Ireland, examined claims of historical sexual abuse.
title: Scouting Ireland review uncovers child abuse cover up
title_page: Scouting Ireland review uncovers child abuse cover up - BBC News
maintext: Mr Elliot added: "It must be recognised and accepted by all that there is no greater priority for scouting today than the safeguarding of the young people that are involved with it, and the removal of anyone from scouting who places them at risk."
